annotations: And yet another familiar face will grace `` the West Wing '' in the incoming Bush administration -- Mary Matalin , a former senior campaign aide to President - elect Bush 's father .
She 'll serve as assistant to the President and counselor to Vice President - elect Dick Cheney .
No comment tonight on his wife 's new job , from Democratic strategist James Carville , who , after all , masterminded Bill Clinton 's successful race against President Bush in 1992 .
